      "writtenOn": "2019-10-21T23:37:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It shouldn\u0027t have issue here, an important fact is the total number of bits is a multiple of 8, you might be worried that we lost some 0 bits here, but since the leftover bit isn\u0027t more than 8, in the decoding step, the lost 0 bits will automatically be added back.\n\nLet me know if I missed anything.",
